ccessible_resources</a></li></ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n     <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary>Workshop de extensões</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"https://extensionworkshop.com/documentation/develop/\">Desenvolver</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://extensionworkshop.com/documentation/publish/\">Publicar</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://extensionworkshop.com/documentation/manage/\">Gerenciar</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://extensionworkshop.com/documentation/enterprise/\">Empreendimento</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n    <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/Contact_us\"><strong>Contate-Nos</strong></a></li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary>Canais</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"https://blog.mozilla.org/addons\">Blog de complementos</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://discourse.mozilla.org/c/add-ons\">Fóruns complementares</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://chat.mozilla.org/#/room/%23addons:mozilla.org\">Add-ons chat</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n  </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>Permite que extensões do navegador alterem seu tema.</p>\n<p>Para usar esta API, uma extensão deve solicitar a <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json/permissions\">permission</a> (permissão) de \"tema\" em seu arquivo <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json\">manifest.json</a>.</p>\n<blockquote>\n  <p><strong>Nota:</strong> Quando configuramos um arquivo de plano de fundo, devemos declarar a <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json/permissions\">permission</a> (permissão) de \"tema\" e, assim sendo, nós não poderemos usar a função <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json/theme\">theme</a> (de tema), se esta for incompatível.</p>\n</blockquote>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"tipo","title":"Tipo","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"theme.theme\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/theme/Theme\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">theme.Theme (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Representa o conteúdo de um tema.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"funções","title":"Funções","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"theme.getcurrent\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/theme/getCurrent\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">theme.getCurrent() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Obtém o tema atual do navegador.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"theme.update\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/theme/update\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">theme.update() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Atualiza o tema do navegador.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"theme.reset\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/theme/reset\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">theme.reset() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Remove quaisquer atualizações de temas feitas em uma chamada para <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/theme/update\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">theme.update() (en-US)</a>.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"evento","title":"Evento","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"theme.onupdated\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/theme/onUpdated\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">theme.onUpdated (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Disparada quando o navegador tiver sido alterado.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"compatibilidade_com_navegadores","isH3":false,"query":"webextensions.api.theme","dataURL":"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/theme/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example_extensions","title":"Example extensions","isH3":false,"content":"<ul><li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/webextensions-examples/tree/master/dynamic-theme\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">dynamic-theme</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/webextensions-examples/tree/master/private-browsing-theme\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">private-browsing-theme</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/webextensions-examples/tree/master/theme-integrated-sidebar\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">theme-integrated-sidebar</a></li></ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Tipo","id":"tipo"},{"text":"Funções","id":"funções"},{"text":"Evento","id":"evento"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"compatibilidade_com_navegadores"},{"text":"Example extensions","id":"example_extensions"}],"summary":"Permite que extensões do navegador alterem seu tema.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"theme","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"theme","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"theme","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/mozilla/add-ons/webextensions/api/theme","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/mozilla/add-ons/webextensions/api/theme/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla","title":"Mozilla"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons","title":"Complementos"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions","title":"Extensões do navegador"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API","title":"JavaScript APIs"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/theme","title":"tema"}],"pageTitle":"tema - Mozilla | MDN","noIndexing":false}}